20 REM THE SEQUENCE - BASIC IMPLEMENTATION
30 REM A MONUMENT TO ORDINAL PROGRESSION
40 REM ******************************************
50 REM
60 REM INITIALIZE VARIABLES
70 DIM TERMS(32, 2): REM ORDINAL TERMS (EXPONENT, COEFFICIENT)
80 DIM DISPLAY$(200): REM STRING BUFFER FOR DISPLAY  
